text: Guspini (Gùspini) is a town and comune (municipality) in the Province of Sud Sardegna in Sardinia, Italy. As of 2016, 11,870 people lived there. Its area is 174.67 km². It is 130 meters above sea level. == References == == Other websites == Category:Communes of the Province of South Sardinia
title: Guspini
